Package main

Class dataStructure

java.lang.Object
main.dataStructure
Direct Known Subclasses:
Client, Journey
public class dataStructure
extends java.lang.Object
The dataStructure class holds all information used for the methods in Client and Journey.

The dataStructure class contains maps with information about clients and journeys along with methods for generating/storing data.

2020-05-06
